，大多对特朗普政府持正面立场。 经济数据避重就轻 ：在「民生负担」板块中，应用只强调了鸡蛋、牛奶、面包等食品价格的同比下降，却对近期汽油价格飙升的情况刻意回避。 互动功能名不副实 ：社交板块设有「给特朗普总统发信息」的按钮，点击后会自动生成「史上最伟大总统！」的预设文本，最终目的却是引导用户订阅营销信息。尽管新闻稿提到用户可 「 直接向政府表达意见和反馈 」，但应用实际功能中并无此设计。 执法举报功能引发争议 ：最引人注目的是，在 「 联系方式 」 板块中，用户甚至可以直接向美国移民与海关执法局（Immigration and Customs Enforcement, ICE）提交举报信息。 虽然能在一个平台上获取特朗普政府的所有公告确实方便，但白宫应用程序本质上更像一个跳转链接集合，大多数功能最终都会打开外部网站。传统上，总统换届后，白宫在各大社交媒体平台的官方账号会移交给新任政府使用。至于特朗普卸任后这款应用的命运如何，目前尚难预料，但回顾特朗普 RX 网站（TrumpRx，据称曾直接销售处方药）、特朗普移动（Trump Mobile，特朗普集团推出的手机品牌）乃至特朗普大学（Trump University，一所未经认证的“教育 白宫官方 App 上架，美媒点评：既怪异又多余"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-55c7ca48d4e9ab2da2d4da072502fba1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021523862542624218"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODk0MDcxMiCuiaLOBjAAOKUBQBRyEzIwMjE1MjM4NjI1NDI2MjQyMTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1774924107.279327", "card_id": "Q_2021653154379376042", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "就侵权演唱李荣浩原创歌曲事件，如果你是单依纯的公关团队成员，你会怎样平息这场风波？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b0cdb6fa6f26ea4d9f4c59b4e694da36.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "91 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021653154379376042"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODk0NjQ0NiCY+qPOBjAAOBxAFXITMjAyMTY1MzE1NDM3OTM3NjA0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1774924107.279746", "card_id": "Q_49988768", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 246}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待「1990 年的大专学历的含金量相当于今天的 211」这一说法？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今天听到长辈的这种说法，希望知道 1990 年的高考是否如题目所说含金量十分高？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bf9a7c9c62a47b74939187367b56cb86_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/49988768"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCDEyMjEyMjgxIPX6+L0FMAA4qgNAFnIINDk5ODg3Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1774924107.280243", "card_id": "Q_1999151801996423693", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马斯克多次提到的「第一性原理」究竟是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "马斯克在特斯拉降电池成本、 SpaceX 做火箭回收时，多次提到用「第一性原理」 打破行业惯性，想请教：第一性原理的准确定义是什么？是否有商业领域（如内容创作、消费品牌）的具体应用案例？普通人如何训练这种思维，避免陷入「类比推理」的惯性？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9130768b77b64849ccc18a080c982951.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1999151801996423693"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODIwNDY5NyCUwtzLBjAAOOoDQBdyEzE5OTkxNTE4MDE5OTY0MjM2OTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1774924107.281286", "card_id": "Q_2021584407622940446", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中东冲突震动全球半导体供应链，氦气现货暴涨超 50%，为什么会这样？氦气涨价，会影响什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中东战事 中东氦气断供冲击全球半导体产业 IT 之家 3 月 27 日消息，集邦咨询 trendforce 今天（3 月 27 日）发布博文，报道称受中东冲突影响，全球半导体供应链拉响警报，氦气的现货价格飙升超 50%，三星、 SK 海力士等韩国芯片巨头正不计成本抢夺库存。 消息称中东冲突已直接影响全球半导体产业，芯片行业正密切监控供应链动态，担忧氦气、稀释剂、乙醇和异丙醇等关键材料断供。虽然这些材料在芯片总成本中占比不高，但断供风险已成为行业最大隐患。 氦气供应危机首当其冲，现货价格涨幅已突破 50%。IT 之家援引博文介绍，氦气是液化天然气（LNG）的副产品，全球约三分之一的供应量严重依赖卡塔尔。 据卡塔尔能源公司高管透露，本次冲突已波及该国约 17% 的 LNG 出口产能。业内评估，即使各方达成停火协议，修复受损设施仍需数年，氦气短缺将演变为中长期风险。 相比韩国厂商的被动局面，台积电和联电因具备 60% 至 75% 的氦气回收率，大幅降低了进口依赖，然而这道防线并非坚不可摧。 不过晶圆厂每天仍需补充约 25% 的氦气损耗。更关键的是，氦气回收系统属于高耗能设备，若全球 LNG 供应受阻引发区域性限电，台积电的回收效率将大幅缩水。 除氦气外，国际油价攀升也全面推高了半导体石化类材料的生产成本。用于清除残留光刻胶的稀释剂首当其冲。杜邦、陶氏和 LG 化学等上游供应商已发布涨价通知，核心原料丙二醇甲醚（PGME）及相关衍生物的价格暴涨 40% 至 50%。受此影响，下游化工厂计划在 4 月将出货价格上调约 20%。中东冲突震动全球半导体供应链：氦气现货暴涨超 50%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-aead074097970378d67c0982917fbccd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2021584407622940446"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODk0NDEyMiCS+qLOBjAAOG5AGHITMjAyMTU4NDQwNzYyMjk0MDQ0NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1774924107.283657", "card_id": "Q_2017757623496225077", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为何西方人喜欢在家里挂一个动物头的标本？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有的刮鹿，有的挂熊，甚至有挂狮子老虎的。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017757623496225077"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODgxMDE3MSCZouvNBjAAOC5AGXITMjAxNzc1NzYyMzQ5NjIyNTA3N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1774924107.284302", "card_id": "Q_287895429", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 543}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么是你去了天津才知道的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-21b27e18e2abd3c28e2acea5752df531.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/287895429"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCDI2MjUzNzY3IInVhNsFMAA4mw1AGnIJMjg3ODk1NDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1774924107.284837", "card_id": "Q_657904190", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 929}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "以前没有手机导航的时候，怎么开车啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "现在开车出门几乎都是直接搜索目的地，然后全程跟着手机地图导航走。有时某个路段大桥 路段 立交 叠加在一块，有个实时导航都开得迷迷糊糊，就是很想知道 以前没手机导航的时候，司机不熟悉路况，不认路要怎么开车啊？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4a90d912d24b754a331fe7393c023a4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657904190"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTEwODQ3ODc2NiC3sfCyBjAAOMsIQBtyCTY1NzkwNDE5MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1774924107.285821", "card_id": "Q_2017997183467672489", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 25}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "交大学生推出校内恋爱匹配平台，65 道题筛选对象，算法真的靠谱吗？「系统派单」和「父母严选」哪个更好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 10 日，交大学生发布了一款自主开发的校内专属恋爱匹配平台 SJTU Date。上线不到一周，注册人数已超 7000 人。数据显示，截至 3 月 16 日中午 12 时，报名首轮匹配的人数超 4000 人；17 日晚，2400 人成功匹配。当下，国内婚恋话题热气腾腾，社交媒体上，由父母催婚引发代际冲突的现象亦屡见不鲜。有趣的是，平台算法用于筛选的问卷问题，恰恰代为执行了父母们在相亲中设置的部分标准。而年轻人缘何选择拥抱前者、拒绝后者？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017997183467672489"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODgxODgzMSC14O7NBjAAOC5AHHITMjAxNzk5NzE4MzQ2NzY3MjQ4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1774924107.286940", "card_id": "Q_1992755606508028276", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在 ai 盛行的时代，一个软件工程专业的本科生该如何规划自己的大学四年？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题。题主现在软件工程专业读大一，一个学期读下来，题主意识到学校的教学可能已经与当下社会需求产生巨大脱节。日常课程学习中，大部分学生使用 ai 写代码（甚至不是「辅助」，而是直接复制粘贴）。就题主观察，身边大部分同学目前并不能脱离 ai 自己写一个几百行的小项目（这里指简单经典的游戏，比如坦克大战，带棋谱带人机对战的翻转棋等）。在一门选修课中老师也提到 ai 对这个专业的冲击非常大。如果 ai 完全能覆盖掉我日常学习的内容，我是否可以放掉一些东西，而有选择地学习其他内容，或者着意去学习某些技能？当下作为一名软工学生，该如何规划自己的大学四年呢？希望得到各位大佬的解答。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c5ca27b9a1baafe7175d2601e0f73ed6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1992755606508028276"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI3vbA8LC+tLt1EAMaCTExODAwMzg1NiCouP/KBjAAOGtAHXITMTk5Mjc1NTYwNjUwODAyODI3NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"t